---
title: SuperQuick Asian-Inspired Chicken Tacos with Peanuts and Hot Honey Drizzle
description: The flavours in these super-quick, Asian-inspired chicken tacos are out of this world! Ginger, garlic, soy and hot honey are evenly matched with refreshing cabbage slaw for a contrast you'll be craving for days after.

